Notes field 

Gaps & Enhancements Needed 

1.1 Make TTT a Mandatory Gate, Not a Log 

Right now, TTT is informational. It should become governance-linked. 

Add fields: 

Onboarding Event ID (mandatory, dropdown from Roadmap) 

TTT Type: 

Initial Enablement 

Refresher 

Optional / Awareness 

TTT Required (Yes / No) 

Rule: 

A lab cannot be marked “Released” unless: 

TTT Required = No 
OR 

At least one TTT session = Completed 

Why: 
Prevents labs going live without trainer readiness. 

